3.1.8 strxns-0.9.2.4.rc3
------------------------

The `STREAMS XNS' (`strxns-0.9.2.4.rc3') package provides Communications Data
Link Interface (CDI), Data Link Provider Interface (DLPI) and Network Provider
Interface (NPI) drivers, modules, header files, documentation and specification
reprints.

This package contains drivers, modules and header files that were split off
from the `Linux STREAMS' release so that they could be corrected and used with
`Linux Fast-STREAMS'.  In particular, the standard headers files (`sys/cdi.h',
`sys/dlpi.h' and `sys/npi.h') that formed part of the original `LiS' releases
from GCOM (http://www.gcom.com/) releases of `LiS' contained errors.

This package also provides additional DLPI and NPI drivers that were not
present in any `LiS' release.

This package is complete but not completely tested.  This package relies upon
the present of the following packages also included in the OpenSS7 Master
Package:

  1. `Linux Fast-STREAMS' (`streams-0.7a.6.rc3') or

  2. `Linux STREAMS' (`LiS-2.18.4.rc3'); and,

  3. `STREAMS Compatibility Modules' (`strcompat-0.9.2.4.rc3')

This package is contained in the `strxns' subdirectory in the OpenSS7 Master
Package source distribution.  See the installation and reference manual in the
`strxns/doc' directory for more information on this sub-package.


